OL,3,CMen arrested at airport after fleeing
OL,4,Cthe country following road race death
OL,6,FTwo men who killed another man while
OL,7,Ftaking part in a road race have
OL,8,Ffinally been caught and jailed - after
OL,9,Ffleeing the country for nine months.
OL,11,FOsama Saeed and Asgar Taj went on the
OL,12,Frun partway through their trial for
OL,13,Fcausing the death of Asad Rashid by
OL,14,Fdangerous driving.
OL,16,FThe trio, along with Mohammad Zubair
OL,17,FChaudhry, had been taking part in a
OL,18,Fdrag race on the A34, near Wilmslow,
OL,19,FCheshire, in September 2020 when they
OL,20,Fall crashed into a roundabout.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
