OL,6,FRashid, who was on a motorcycle, was
OL,7,Fhit by one of the cars and died at the
OL,8,Fscene.
OL,10,FAfter fleeing abroad, Saeed and Taj
OL,11,Fsubsequently pleaded guilty to the
OL,12,Fcharge after dialling into the court
OL,13,Ffrom abroad.
OL,15,FBut both failed to return to court for
OL,16,Ftheir sentencing, and were sentenced
OL,17,Fin their absence.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
