OL,6,FSaeed, 32, of Manningham, Bradford,
OL,7,Fwas jailed for 12 years and Taj, 35,
OL,8,Fof Heather Grove, Bradford, were both
OL,9,Ffinally re-arrested by police at
OL,10,FManchester Airport on 8 July after
OL,11,Ftravelling to the UK on a flight from
OL,12,FAbu Dhabi.
OL,14,FChaudhry, 31 of Kingsway, Cheadle, who
OL,15,Falso pleaded guilty, is still on the
OL,16,Frun.
