OL,6,FDuring the trial, Manchester Minshull
OL,7,FStreet Court was told the four men
OL,8,Ftravelled to Cheshire on 15 September
OL,9,F2020 to take part in a race.
OL,11,FChaudry was driving an Audi R8, Saeed
OL,12,Fin an Audi R3, while Taj and Rashid
OL,13,Fwere riding Suzuki motorbikes.
OL,15,FVideo footage shows the group using
OL,16,Fthe traffic lights as a starting flag,
OL,17,Fracing off as the lights changed, with
OL,18,Fthe level of acceleration putting them
OL,19,Fout of sight within seconds.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
