OL,4,Cthe country following road race death
OL,6,FAs the group approached the Total
OL,7,FFitness roundabout, they were
OL,8,Ftravelling too quickly and all four
OL,9,Fcollided with the middle, narrowly
OL,10,Fmissing other members of the public.
OL,12,FChaudhry's Audi R8 hit first, with the
OL,13,Fimpact tearing off the underside of
OL,14,Fthe engine and sending it flying 135
OL,15,Fmetres further down the A34.
OL,17,FThe two motorbikes and the Audi RS3
OL,18,Fthen hit the roundabout at about the
OL,19,Fsame time, with Taj and Rashid both
OL,20,Fbecoming unseated from their bikes.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
