OL,6,FTaj sustained a number of serious
OL,7,Finjuries including fracturing his
OL,8,Fright arm and fractures to his left
OL,9,Ffoot.
OL,11,FRashid was struck by the RS3 as it hit
OL,12,Fthe central reservation, leaving him
OL,13,Ftrapped him by the vehicle, he died at
OL,14,Fthe scene as a result of his injuries.
