OL,6,FMembers of the public stopped to help
OL,7,Fthe injured men and, the court was
OL,8,Ftold, as one of them approached Taj as
OL,9,Fhe lay on the roundabout, they noticed
OL,10,Fhe was clearly deleting files from
OL,11,FInstagram, before then deleting the
OL,12,Fapp itself in an attempt to destroy
OL,13,Fevidence.
OL,15,FDuring the investigation by the
OL,16,FSerious and Complex Collision
OL,17,FInvestigation Unit at Cheshire Police,
OL,18,Fofficers found on the night of the
OL,19,Fcollision Taj, Saeed and Rashid had
OL,20,Fall spoken with Chaudhury, discussing
OL,21,Fwhere to meet up and race.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
