OL,3,CMen arrested at airport after fleeing
OL,4,Cthe country following road race death
OL,6,FChaudhury suggested that roads in
OL,7,FCheshire would be good as the police
OL,8,Fdid not know them, the court heard.
OL,10,FChaudhury also had a number of "Trophy
OL,11,Fvideos" on his phone showing him and
OL,12,Fothers known to him driving at high
OL,13,Fspeeds on roads across the country.
OL,15,FOne video showed him driving at 139mph
OL,16,Fin a 40mph zone on the A34 Kingsway
OL,17,FGrange, near to his home address, a
OL,18,Fbuilt-up area with a school and lots
OL,19,Fof residential houses.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
