OL,3,CMen arrested at airport after fleeing
OL,4,Cthe country following road race death
OL,6,FA further video was found showing
OL,7,FChaudhury driving at 192mph on a
OL,8,Fmotorway, the video also showed him
OL,9,Fbragging with others while driving his
OL,10,FAudi R8.
OL,12,FChaudhry was sentenced to 10-years and
OL,13,Fseven months in prison, Saeed was
OL,14,Fjailed for 12 years and Taj was also
OL,15,Fsentenced to 12 years behind bars.
OL,17,FCheshire Police released 'trophy
OL,18,Ffootage' of the groups races, and
OL,19,Ffootage of the devastating scene left
OL,20,Fby the crash in September 2020.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
