OL,3,CMen arrested at airport after fleeing
OL,4,Cthe country following road race death
OL,6,FFollowing the sentencing Sergeant
OL,7,FAndrew Dennison, of Cheshire police,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Driving is a privilege, not a
OL,9,Fright, and it comes with great
OL,10,Fresponsibility to act within the rules
OL,11,Flaid down when you pass your test.
OL,13,F"The sad death of Asad Rashid that
OL,14,Fnight shows the catastrophic
OL,15,Fconsequences that will happen when
OL,16,Fthese rules are ignored.
OL,18,F"Taj, Chaudhury and Saeed all came to
OL,19,FWilmslow with Rashid knowing they were
OL,20,Fcoming to race on the roads around
OL,21,FCheshire.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
