OL,3,CMen arrested at airport after fleeing
OL,4,Cthe country following road race death
OL,6,F"They drove in a manner that put
OL,7,Feveryone around them at great risk and
OL,8,Fthe inevitable conclusion of this
OL,9,Fdriving was a serious collision that
OL,10,Fclaimed the life of Rashid.
OL,12,F"The knowledge of the group coming to
OL,13,Frace and the actions they undertook
OL,14,Fmeant that they were all culpable in
OL,15,Fthe death of Rashid and as a result
OL,16,Fare all guilty of causing his death by
OL,17,Fdriving dangerously.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
