OL,3,CMen arrested at airport after fleeing
OL,4,Cthe country following road race death
OL,6,F"As a result of the selfish and
OL,7,Fdangerous actions taken that night
OL,8,Ffour families have been torn apart.
OL,9,FRashid is now dead, while Chaudhry,
OL,10,FSaeed and Taj have all been handed
OL,11,Fsignificant prison sentences.
OL,13,F"None of the men have shown any
OL,14,Fremorse for their actions, and that
OL,15,Ffact that they failed to attend the
OL,16,Fhearing demonstrates a total lack of
OL,17,Faccountability.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
