OL,6,F"While Rashid was not wholly innocent,
OL,7,Fhe did not deserve to die and if
OL,8,Fanything can be achieved from this
OL,9,Fcase, I hope it acts as a warning to
OL,10,Fothers and prevents any needless
OL,11,Fcollisions like this from occurring
OL,12,Fagain."
